"     <br>",
"      * Values are mean &plusmn; 1 standard deviation.",
"      <br>",
"       Note that splenectomy corrected the anemia and reduced the reticulocyte percentage almost to normal in patients with hereditary spherocytosis, but did not alter the spherocytic changes, as reflected by the increased values for MCHC, either in the reticulocytes or the mature red cells.",
"      </br>",
